				<td colspan="2"><span>im currently watching several threads regarding this and working on it myself. it is possible but has not yet been completed. if your looking to do this i can give you a little hint what i know your gonna need when i write the completed guide. 
<br />

<br />
plane of nightmare - agony mephit heart, found inside the tunnel underwater near the hobgoblins
<br />

<br />
plane of valor - holy water or something like that off of  the guards and seargants. there no faction and they arnt that hard. you also need a crystal spider brain from a lucid spider which runs around the wastelands.
<br />

<br />
Plane of Innovation - perilium which is some kind of metal found on the tougher mobs in the zone. if youve gotten this please post what mob droped it.
<br />

<br />
need some stuff from other planes and you need to combine this stuff. no one has completed the quest so  dont want to encourage anyone to go further and have them waste their items on a bad turn in. i myself am gonna wait for absolute confirmation. ill keep this thread current as best i can.
<br />

