				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: alternative entrance to tier 3 zones<a name="2084"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Nov 18 02 6:04 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Here's some information that was posted on my guild's message board about getting access into Decay:
<br />

<br />

<br />
=============================================
<br />
Here is more info for those who can't make the Raid and want to get into Crypt of Decay
<br />

<br />
Grimror Plaguebringer is an Ogre in silver platemail that was roaming near the entrance to plane of disease, got him to talk to me, he has a quest 
<br />

<br />
You say, 'Hail, Grimror Plaguebringer'
<br />
Grimror Plaguebringer says 'Grimror no have time ta talk. Gots stuffs ta do.'
<br />
You say, 'what stuffs?'
<br />
Grimror Plaguebringer says 'I wuz sent here by Zulort to, err. . . To gadder some alchemy type stuffs. Him have big plan, and need me to travel lots.'
<br />
You say, 'who is zulort'
<br />
You say, 'what big plans?'
<br />
Grimror Plaguebringer laughs. 'Me not tell you dat! Grimror keep secrets secret. You gonna help Grimror or no?'
<br />
You say, 'I will help grimror'
<br />
Grimror Plaguebringer says 'Dat good! Grimror been getting compon ents for dayz now and Grimror still not finushed. You gonna get dem tings fur me?'
<br />
You say, 'what tings?'
<br />
Grimror Plaguebringer says 'Grimror need bile, dat stuff es strong here! But Grimror keent seem to git eet all. Bile comz from da leetle bugs. Keel little bugs, and geeve Grimror dere leetel bodiez and Grimror give yuuz anyting dat yuuz want. Dere be four leetel buggiez dat Grimror still neez, seegeen, scaveen, genereen, and harroon. Yuuz bring Grimror dere skinz and Grimror geeve you anyting yuuz want.'
<br />

<br />
---
<br />

<br />
The four mobs are sengian, harrion, scaevian, and generian larva.
<br />

<br />
PH for Harrion larva = a malarian larva(not larvae like all the others, spawns near zone in a bit out near flies)
<br />
PH for Generian larva = a planarian larva(again just larva, spawns east of castle east of river near pussling camps)
<br />
PH for Scaevian larva = a Tsetsian Pupa(just pupa, not pupal, spawns a bit east of generian)
<br />
PH for Sengian larva = (unknown at this point)
<br />

<br />

<br />
Reward is:
<br />

<br />
Bangle of Disease Warding
<br />
MAGIC ITEM LORE ITEM NO DROP 
<br />
AC: 7
<br />
Effect: Resist Disease (Must Equip. Casting Time: Instant)
<br />
WT: 0.3 Size: SMALL
<br />
Class: NONE
<br />
Race: NONE
<br />

<br />
It identifies as 
<br />
You begin casting Identify.
<br />
Item Lore: With this, you may pass into Decay.
<br />

<br />
Bangle of Disease warding has been added to your key ring.
<br />
And this is what /key showed
<br />
Grimror's Bracer grants access to the Ruins Lxanvom.
<br />
</span></td>
