<br />

<br />
The Spider Brain... I was fighting at &quot;DD&quot; (the Dragon Door) in PoV a couple nights ago, We only saw the Lucid Spider once, and no brain, but we saw the Luminii crawler three times consecutively, all three times with a brain. The Luminii Crawler seems to be able to spawn anywhere in a number of spawn spots in place of a normal PH.
<br />

<br />
The Perillium seems to only drop off the buzz saw models as mentioned. The little level 46 DC mobs at the entrance don't drop it I think. The reason you see it rarely is because mostly only &quot;named&quot; mobs have that model.</span></td>
